# Xcode / iOS — per github/gitignore canonical Global/Xcode + Swift templates
## User settings (per-developer UI state — never commit)
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcuserstatedata

## Build artefacts
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.dSYM
