## Playgrounds
timeline.xctimeline
playground.xcworkspace

## Swift Package Manager
## NOTE: Package.resolved IS committed (kept out of this list) so dependency
## versions are reproducible across machines and CI — Apple's recommendation.
.build/
.swiftpm/

## CocoaPods / Carthage / fastlane (not used today; listed pre-emptively)
Pods/
Carthage/Build/
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots/**/*.png
fastlane/test_output

# Generated Prisma client (regenerated on install)
backend/prisma/migrations/.cache/

# Local backup artefacts
*.dump
*.dump.age
*.tar.age

# Coverage / test
coverage/
.nyc_output/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Local SSH keys / sensitive material — never commit
claude
claude.pub
*.pem

# Claude Code per-machine overrides (CLAUDE.local.md, .claude/settings.local.json,
# any *.local.md). The shared CLAUDE.md and .claude/ ARE tracked — this rule
# only blocks the personal-override variants.
*.local.md
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/.cache/
